aurangzeb is an indian action thriller film written and directed by atul sabharwal . the film stars arjun kapoor in the lead role , along with prithviraj sukumaran , sashaa agha , swara bhaskar in pivotal roles , while jackie shroff , rishi kapoor , amrita singh , sikander kher and kavi shastri play supporting characters . the film is produced and distributed by aditya chopra under his studio yash raj films . the theatrical trailer was unveiled on 3 april 2013 , and the film released on 17 may 2013 . the film was commercially successful .